[
    {
        "text": "I’m Neil Jordan.",
        "start": 0.875,
        "duration": 0.785
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m the director of “Greta.”",
        "start": 1.66,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Frances, played\nby Chloë Moretz,",
        "start": 3.86,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "is a waitress in this\nNew York restaurant,",
        "start": 6.26,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "and she’s being pursued\nby this woman, played",
        "start": 8.06,
        "duration": 3.27
    },
    {
        "text": "by Isabelle Huppert,\ncalled Greta.",
        "start": 11.33,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "She becomes this\nclingy friend/monster.",
        "start": 13.61,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "One of the final straws\nof Greta’s attempts",
        "start": 16.17,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "to invade Frances's life\nis when she books a table",
        "start": 19.01,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "at the restaurant she works.",
        "start": 22.1,
        "duration": 1.615
    },
    {
        "text": "“Is there a problem?”",
        "start": 23.715,
        "duration": 0.883
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes.",
        "start": 24.598,
        "duration": 0.249
    },
    {
        "text": "This woman has\nbeen harassing me",
        "start": 24.847,
        "duration": 0.994
    },
    {
        "text": "and you need to\nask her to leave.”",
        "start": 25.841,
        "duration": 1.417
    },
    {
        "text": "“I’m afraid she\nhas a reservation.”",
        "start": 27.258,
        "duration": 1.674
    },
    {
        "text": "“What kind of\nservice is this?”",
        "start": 28.932,
        "duration": 2.063
    },
    {
        "text": "So we designed the\nrestaurant specifically",
        "start": 30.995,
        "duration": 1.815
    },
    {
        "text": "around this scene —",
        "start": 32.81,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "the shape of it,\nthe table lights,",
        "start": 34.37,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "the pools of light from\nabove, and the mirrors.",
        "start": 36.68,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "We wanted an environment\nwhere the traffic",
        "start": 39.41,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "of the waiters to and\nfro the tables was fluid.",
        "start": 41.57,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "We would allow for these\nlong, fluid kind of shots.",
        "start": 45.81,
        "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Everything was designed\nto kind of ratchet up",
        "start": 49.29,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "the humiliation of the\ncentral character, Frances.",
        "start": 52.73,
        "duration": 2.811
    },
    {
        "text": "[music]",
        "start": 55.541,
        "duration": 3.946
    },
    {
        "text": "“I’ll start with\nthe crab bisque",
        "start": 59.487,
        "duration": 1.333
    },
    {
        "text": "and a small green salad.”",
        "start": 60.82,
        "duration": 1.882
    },
    {
        "text": "“Why are you doing this?”",
        "start": 62.702,
        "duration": 1.494
    },
    {
        "text": "“Because we have to talk.”",
        "start": 64.196,
        "duration": 2.034
    },
    {
        "text": "“I have nothing\nto say to you.”",
        "start": 66.23,
        "duration": 1.893
    },
    {
        "text": "The clothes that the central\ncharacter, Greta, wears",
        "start": 68.123,
        "duration": 2.167
    },
    {
        "text": "was extremely important.",
        "start": 70.29,
        "duration": 1.15
    },
    {
        "text": "We had a lot of discussion\nabout the costume —",
        "start": 71.44,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "the sophistication,\nthe Frenchness of it.",
        "start": 74.31,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "We managed to get a great\ncostume from Karl Lagerfeld",
        "start": 77.07,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "and Chanel.",
        "start": 80.97,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "Those elements really\nwere the scene, you know?",
        "start": 82.59,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "I mean, Isabelle’s\nsophistication,",
        "start": 85.23,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "her Frenchness.",
        "start": 86.85,
        "duration": 0.993
    },
    {
        "text": "“If you say so.",
        "start": 87.843,
        "duration": 0.937
    },
    {
        "text": "Cherie — “",
        "start": 88.78,
        "duration": 1.713
    },
    {
        "text": "“Do not call me that.”",
        "start": 90.493,
        "duration": 1.373
    },
    {
        "text": "“[speaking french].",
        "start": 91.866,
        "duration": 1.184
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s what you\nare, my darling.”",
        "start": 93.05,
        "duration": 1.797
    },
    {
        "text": "And the fact that,\nat a certain point,",
        "start": 94.847,
        "duration": 1.583
    },
    {
        "text": "she reveals herself\nto be Hungarian.",
        "start": 96.43,
        "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
        "text": "- [speaking hungarian].",
        "start": 98.26,
        "duration": 2.558
    },
    {
        "text": "Because she is a\ncharacter with about",
        "start": 100.818,
        "duration": 1.542
    },
    {
        "text": "four different layers\nto her, and I suppose",
        "start": 102.36,
        "duration": 2.832
    },
    {
        "text": "this is a scene where all\nthose layers are expressed.",
        "start": 105.192,
        "duration": 2.208
    },
    {
        "text": "She knows how to order a wine.",
        "start": 107.4,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "She knows how to hold a\ntable in a restaurant.",
        "start": 110.22,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "She knows how to\nembarrass a maître d.",
        "start": 112.74,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "At a certain\npoint, she kind of",
        "start": 115.2,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "reveals herself to be an\nabsolute monster, which",
        "start": 117.18,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "is the fun of the\nscene, which is",
        "start": 119.34,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "the center of the\ncharacter, really.",
        "start": 120.85,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "You know, this\nmonster that sits",
        "start": 122.35,
        "duration": 1.333
    },
    {
        "text": "behind this Frenchness,\nthis sophistication,",
        "start": 123.683,
        "duration": 4.486
    },
    {
        "text": "this kind of politesse.",
        "start": 128.169,
        "duration": 2.131
    },
    {
        "text": "[music]",
        "start": 130.3,
        "duration": 4.446
    },
    {
        "text": "“The Chablis.”",
        "start": 135.404,
        "duration": 1.806
    },
    {
        "text": "“May I?",
        "start": 137.21,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm, a bit like you.",
        "start": 141.662,
        "duration": 3.578
    },
    {
        "text": "Promises a lot,\nthen disappoints.”",
        "start": 145.24,
        "duration": 2.814
    },
    {
        "text": "“O.K.”",
        "start": 148.054,
        "duration": 0.821
    },
    {
        "text": "“I deserve better.”",
        "start": 148.875,
        "duration": 1.345
    },
    {
        "text": "[glass shattering]",
        "start": 150.22,
        "duration": 0.75
    },
    {
        "text": "[gasping]",
        "start": 150.97,
        "duration": 0.995
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s also a very\nphysical scene.",
        "start": 151.965,
        "duration": 2.085
    },
    {
        "text": "And in scenes like this,\npeople can get hurt.",
        "start": 154.05,
        "duration": 2.858
    },
    {
        "text": "“ — to us.”",
        "start": 156.908,
        "duration": 0.792
    },
    {
        "text": "“Are you a child?”",
        "start": 157.7,
        "duration": 0.75
    },
    {
        "text": "“No.",
        "start": 158.45,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "You’re the child.",
        "start": 158.95,
        "duration": 0.75
    },
    {
        "text": "You need to mature.",
        "start": 159.7,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "You need a mother to hold you.",
        "start": 160.71,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "You lost someone, and\nyou are afraid to love.",
        "start": 161.96,
        "duration": 1.896
    },
    {
        "text": "We both know its true.”",
        "start": 163.856,
        "duration": 1.086
    },
    {
        "text": "“Don’t you dare talk\nto me about my mother.”",
        "start": 164.942,
        "duration": 1.932
    },
    {
        "text": "“Darling, don’t\nyou understand?",
        "start": 166.874,
        "duration": 1.292
    },
    {
        "text": "She had to die.",
        "start": 168.166,
        "duration": 1.003
    },
    {
        "text": "(SHOUTING) She had to\ndie for us to meet!”",
        "start": 169.169,
        "duration": 2.661
    },
    {
        "text": "So I had to set up an\nenvironment and a context",
        "start": 171.83,
        "duration": 2.85
    },
    {
        "text": "whereby she could express\nherself physically,",
        "start": 174.68,
        "duration": 3.18
    },
    {
        "text": "throw things around,\nstruggle with grown men.",
        "start": 177.86,
        "duration": 3.93
    },
    {
        "text": "So, I mean, in this scene, the\nfact that she felt physically",
        "start": 181.79,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "safe was tremendously\nimportant",
        "start": 184.67,
        "duration": 2.19
    },
    {
        "text": "to her and to the scene\nitself, I suppose.",
        "start": 186.86,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "[music]",
        "start": 189.23,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "“Leave me alone!”",
        "start": 192.98,
        "duration": 1.698
    }
]